  "original_title": "Isipathana crowned winners of Schools Rugby League 2022",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Isipathana crowned winners of Schools Rugby League 2022",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st);\u00a0Isipathana School Colombo were crowned the 2022 Schools Rugby League winners today (14), defeating the\u00a0defending Champions Royal College Colombo.",
        "The decisive Super Round encounter to decide the Champions of the Schools Rugby League tournament was held at the Havelock Park in Colombo on Sunday (14).",
        "Isipathana remained undefeated after winning all 6 games held since the preliminary round; Royal lost just one match.",
        "In the first half of the game, Royal College were on top ending the half on 10-6.\u00a0In the second half, Isipathana took over scoring 15 points, while\u00a0Royal managed just 5 points in the second.",
        "Ultimately, the undefeated Isipathana side clinched the match 21 to 15, and regained the Major Milroy Fernando Memorial Shield.",
        "Isipathana College have not won the tournament since 2017; while Royal College were crowned champions in the last tournament which was held in 2019.",
        "Will support from Opposition until Tamil people are satisfied: C.V. Wigneswaran"
      ],
